OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780913124
OL,3,CTwo charged as Smethwick disorder
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FTwo more men have been charged as
OL,7,Fpolice continue to investigate
OL,8,Fdisorder in Smethwick.
OL,10,FIt happened in Foundry Lane, on
OL,11,FTuesday, May 26.
OL,13,FNizar Abdulhafeez, aged 19, and
OL,14,FDiandre Cunningham, aged 18, are both
OL,15,Fcharged with two counts of attempted
OL,16,Fmurder and possession of a bladed
OL,17,Farticle.
OL,19,FThe pair, both from Birmingham, are
OL,20,Fdue at the city's magistrates court on
OL,21,FSaturday, 6 June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
