OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780913124
OL,3,CTwo charged as Smethwick disorder
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FA statement on the West Midlands
OL,7,FPolice website reads: "Our enquiries
OL,8,Fare continuing and we have now charged
OL,9,Ffive men and two teenagers following
OL,10,Fthe disorder on Foundry Lane on 26
OL,11,FMay, which saw two men attending
OL,12,Fhospital with stab wounds.
OL,14,F"We are aware of video footage of the
OL,15,Fincident continuing to circulate, and
OL,16,Fwe would urge people not to share this
OL,17,Fto avoid causing unnecessary distress
OL,18,For potentially prejudicing legal
OL,19,Fproceedings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
