OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1780913124
OL,3,CTwo charged as Smethwick disorder
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,F"A dedicated web page remains in
OL,7,Fplace, where footage can be uploaded
OL,8,Fsecurely to help our investigation."
OL,10,FAnyone with information can contact
OL,11,Fpolice by calling 101 or via Live Chat
OL,12,Fon their website, quoting log 5971 of
OL,13,F26 May.
OL,15,FInformation can also be passed to
OL,16,FCrimestoppers, which is an anonymous
OL,17,Fservice, on 0800 555 111.
